data.value:
Amwaj Beach Club Abu Soma in Safaga offers luxury accommodation with Red Sea views and a private beach. There are 2 pools set within gardens, as well as a spa and fitness centre.
All rooms at Amwaj Beach Club Abu Soma include a private terrace or balcony, overlooking either Soma Bay or the hotel’s pools and gardens.
Air conditioning, satellite TV and a hair dryer are also provided.
At Amwaj Beach Club Abu Soma you can eat at the Culina restaurant. There is also a pool-side bar serving snacks and drinks.
